Question: In at least one image there are at least two people in the sled being pulled by less than five dogs.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: http://alaskanmalamutes.us/images/wwI-nome-dogs-in-france.jpg

Right image URL: http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-L-5Aff4OKuA/U5TDddwfcmI/AAAAAAAAIqk/T_Ukd5_JbSw/s1600/Screen+Shot+2014-06-08+at+1.09.55+PM.png

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many people are in the sled being pulled by less than five dogs?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many people are in the sled being pulled by less than five dogs?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} >= 2 or {ANSWER1} >= 2')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
